Example qPCR data

Source: R/data.r
qpcr_names.Rd

Experimental variables include:

Usage

qpcr_names

Format

qPCR sample names in 96 well format.

Details

  • cell line (wt, mut)

  • gene (IFN, ACTIN)

  • time (0, 12, 24, 48)

  • reverse transcriptase (+, -)

  • replicate (1, 2, 3)

Varaibles are encoded in samples names: cell_time_gene_rt_rep.

Examples

qpcr_names
